  "message": "\ud83d\udc1b Show developer-specific update instructions for dev channel (#1275)\n\n- Show git pull + rebuild command instead of brew/helm for developer channel\n- Display current/latest SHA even without autoUpdateStatus using latestMainSHA\n- Add coding agent tip for AI-assisted updates\n- Keep standard update instructions (browser refresh, brew, helm) for\n  non-developer channels\n\nSigned-off-by: Andrew Anderson <andy@clubanderson.com>",
